430
00:49:27,458 --> 00:49:29,807
Kamu hanya perlu tetap berada di sampingku.

431
00:49:32,895 --> 00:49:36,105
Pegang tanganku, dan kemudian,

432
00:49:36,769 --> 00:49:40,078
